              fill="currentColor"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Madera ecológica certificada</h3>
        <p class="card-description">
          Trabajamos exclusivamente con madera maciza con certificado PEFC de
          bosques sostenibles
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-number">02</div>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg
            width="48"
            height="48"
            viewBox="0 0 48 48"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M38 12H34V10C34 7.8 32.2 6 30 6H18C15.8 6 14 7.8 14 10V12H10C7.8 12 6 13.8 6 16V38C6 40.2 7.8 42 10 42H38C40.2 42 42 40.2 42 38V16C42 13.8 40.2 12 38 12ZM18 10H30V12H18V10ZM38 38H10V16H38V38ZM24 20C20.7 20 18 22.7 18 26C18 29.3 20.7 32 24 32C27.3 32 30 29.3 30 26C30 22.7 27.3 20 24 20ZM24 28C22.9 28 22 27.1 22 26C22 24.9 22.9 24 24 24C25.1 24 26 24.9 26 26C26 27.1 25.1 28 24 28Z"
              fill="currentColor"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Entrega rápida garantizada</h3>
        <p class="card-description">
          Tu pedido sale de fábrica en máximo 1 semana. Compromiso de velocidad
          sin sacrificar calidad
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-number">03</div>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg
            width="48"
            height="48"
            viewBox="0 0 48 48"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M24 6C14.06 6 6 14.06 6 24C6 33.94 14.06 42 24 42C33.94 42 42 33.94 42 24C42 14.06 33.94 6 24 6ZM24 38C16.28 38 10 31.72 10 24C10 16.28 16.28 10 24 10C31.72 10 38 16.28 38 24C38 31.72 31.72 38 24 38ZM25 16H22V26L30.5 31.1L32 28.6L25 24.2V16Z"
              fill="currentColor"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Diseño y fabricación propia</h3>
        <p class="card-description">
          Control total del proceso creativo y productivo para ofrecerte el
          mejor precio del mercado
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-number">04</div>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg
            width="48"
            height="48"
            viewBox="0 0 48 48"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M36 18C36 16.9 35.1 16 34 16H14C12.9 16 12 16.9 12 18V30C12 31.1 12.9 32 14 32H34C35.1 32 36 31.1 36 30V18ZM34 30H14V18H34V30ZM24 20C21.8 20 20 21.8 20 24C20 26.2 21.8 28 24 28C26.2 28 28 26.2 28 24C28 21.8 26.2 20 24 20Z"
              fill="currentColor"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Devoluciones sin costo</h3>
        <p class="card-description">
          15 días para devolver tu compra. Atención personalizada en cada paso
          del proceso
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</SectionContainer>

<style>
  .why-us-wrapper {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  /* Intro Section */
  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .intro-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.8vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text);
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Features Grid - Uniforme y limpio */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-secondary);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-6px);
  }

  /* Card Number */
  .card-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  /* Card Icon */
  .card-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .card-icon {
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: white;
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  /* Card Content */
  .card-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .card-description {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .why-us-wrapper {
      padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-intro {
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 2.25rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .why-us-wrapper {
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .section-intro {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .intro-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .intro-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .card-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      top: 1.25rem;
      right: 1.25rem;
    }

    .card-icon {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
    }

    .card-icon svg {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .card-description {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .why-us-wrapper {
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .section-intro {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .intro-title {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .intro-text {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 1.75rem;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .card-number {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      top: 1rem;
      right: 1rem;
    }

    .card-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
    }

    .card-icon svg {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .card-description {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
</style>
